message:
@rocskincare Derm Correxion Firming Serum Stick has earned a place in my skincare routine.

I really like the touchless stick format. It makes application quick and easy across the face, and the formula feels lightweight, goes on clear. It is such an easy step to add in, especially when you want something simple you can swipe on and keep moving.

